After coming back from a long period of lurking, this is my first attempt at writing an SCP from scratch. I've been reading a lot about Mt. Everest lately and thought it would make a great stomping ground for an SCP, and this idea gradually came together in my mind.

As Everest survivor Lincoln Hall, who inspired the character of  in the interview log, passed away this past week, i'd like to dedicate this SCP to his memory and to all the men and women who have lost their lives on Everest in pursuit of glory.







